milestones.description: Andy Flower has scored 14 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for ZIM breaking Dave Houghton's record
Andy Flower and Grant Flower's 161-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 124 between Andy Flower and Grant Flower
Athar Ali Khan and Habibul Bashar's 37-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Athar Ali Khan and Jahangir Alam
Habibul Bashar has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (3) in ODIs for BAN, going past Aminul Islam's 1
Akram Khan has broken the record for most ODIs (8) as captain for BAN, going past Gazi Ashraf
Andy Flower and Grant Flower's 161-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 145 between Andy Flower and Andy Waller
